Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:01:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the insolent folks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who didn't pay their taxes\Nat the harbor, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Rainbow Mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ape's Concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ape's Concert? It couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.56,0:02:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship graveyard, where once\Nyou enter, you can never get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Residents of the Land of Eternity!\NThe Pumpkin Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! There's nothing but\Nsunken ships, as far as you can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's give this up. It feels like a\Nghost captain might appear at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Ghost captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the Rainbow Mist\Nis the world of the eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final paradise remaining on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's filled with treasures of gold and silver,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where people live forever\Nwithout aging or going hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's written in this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, that's nothing more than a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, you knew that this\Nplace was a ship graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. 50 years ago, I got a\Nshort glimpse of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you knew it, then why come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that, too.\NI've been carrying on my research
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to rescue my friends that\Nwere swallowed up in this mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even became Wetton's dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and put up with the\Nfinger-pointing, to that end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it awesome? There's lots,\Nlots more inside the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go explore some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether this is a paradise or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the "being filled with treasure"\Nthing doesn't appear to be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,altogether untrue, huh, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who would disturb\Nthe rest of the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the cargo, and depart at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:05:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or else, the curse of the dead shall befall you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm s-scared...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hand over the cargo, nice and easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close! You rotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost captain...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're... ghosts... all... right...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that arrow came from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone over there!\NHey, listen to me, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special attack: Fire Star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Akibi!\N--Wait, Rongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Akibi!\N--Take it easy, Rongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're just kids, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, stay away! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm Home!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, thank you for that earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Pumpkin Pirates,\Nand Ape's Concert is our territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release my friends, and turn over\Nthe cargo, if you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapa Nui!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now, if you use that, you'll blow us all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all in the same boat!\NWe live, and die, together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:08:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's go.\N--I'm sorry, Rapa Nui. Rongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapa Nui...? Is that you, Rapa Nui...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... Isoka, and Rongo... It's you, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know me? It's me, Henzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We always used to play together,\Non Cape Luluka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo? You don't mean that Henzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, there's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back! I-I'll blow us up! Stay back, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaboom Mark III. I invented it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a gizmo used for bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, it's a smokescreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the racket...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just now waking up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? For that matter, who's the old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it would take a bit of\Ntime to explain it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they're gone from over here, too.\NWho was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo! Hurry on down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm too scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid over something\Nlike this! We're the Pumpkin Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I grow up, I'm gonna be a real pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Rapa Nui, your father is a marine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to let you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My pop is my pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have adventures in places\Nthat nobody has seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Places nobody has seen before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. There are still lots of things in\Nthis world that nobody knows about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too. I'll be a pirate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll have to fight with\Nother pirates, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone as weak as I am couldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo, you can invent all\Nsorts of things, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll invent the gear that\Nwe'll need for our adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be a pirate, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're easy to convince, Henzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing as friends, and chatting...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent the best days of my life with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day was so bright,\Nit doesn't even compare to treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until that one dreadful event occurred...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've perfected the Kaboom Mark III!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't scare us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure do have a lot of false alarms, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap! The town is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town of Luluka is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is this...?\N--Our town...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn! Burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave nothing of value!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill everyone that opposes us,\Nthe Wetton Pirates! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show the women and children no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, there are still some kids\Nwho haven't run away, are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, guys, once we get to the harbor,\Nthere will be ships there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take one of them, it doesn't\Nmatter which one, and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about Dad, and the others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Do you wanna get killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those brats...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ships...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys earlier must have sunk them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there! We'll get on that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? That one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any others, right? Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to my ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ker-splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all are ready to answer for this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think someone like you\Ncan handle this axe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too cocky, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:16:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a kid! I'm Rapa Nui,\Nthe leader of the Pumpkin Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rapa Nui!\N--It's all right! He's just one man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all join our forces together,\Nand defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Captain, are we setting sail already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rainbow Mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry and turn the helm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get swallowed up inside there,\Nwe won't be able to get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The helm is busted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you... You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you're getting\Nout of here alive anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shoulder's dislocated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapa Nui!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back! Turn the ship back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't! The helm is busted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rainbow Mist... The Rainbow Mist...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rapa Nui!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! Keep going! Don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise, I'll come after you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:18:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a member of the\NPumpkin Pirates, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since, Rapa Nui and\Nthe others have never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that they actually\Nbecame pirates in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but that happened 50 years ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were still just little kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The passage of time within the\NRainbow Mist appears to be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day in here might be equivalent to a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or even a year, in the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, we have to\Nfind a way out of here fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or there'll be no undoing the damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so dense!\NThe same thing that happened
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between those kids earlier and the\Nold man could happen to us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're in here, puttering around,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and the others we left behind\Nwill become old men and women!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Pops, let's go back, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like he said, we don't know how to get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?! Is that right?!\N--So, there's no way back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What have you been listening to, Luffy?!\N--No... There must be a way
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They must have said it... three times now!\N--to get out of Ape's Concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that many times?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, these guys are persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That weapon is a real problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shut your traps! I'll finish you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Lake-sama!\N--Are you all right, Lake-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the ones who chucked that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that matter, wasn't he watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is wearing that thing, and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you, was it you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if we say it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're picking it up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have collected your harbor dues.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now formally welcome\Nyou as a citizen of Luluka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ape's Concert, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Some soldiers said\Nthey saw your ship enter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Rainbow Mist, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what the mayor says, it's\Npiled up with treasure in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that Ape's Concert\Nis a ship graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shipwrecks in there have\Nuntouched cargo all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mayor is after that treasure,\Nwhich is why he has a scientist,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,named Henzo, researching a way\Nto get into Ape's Concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the old man made\Nthis electroshock suit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Pretty damn slick, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy sure likes to talk a lot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't he be content\Nwith just getting the tax?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just stand around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going in into that mist, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But once we go in there,\Nthere's no coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good will getting scared do?\NOur treasure is waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is allowed into Ape's Concert\Nwithout my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Grandpa!\N--You bonehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,0:21:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a poor memory.\NAren't I always telling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are to call me "Mayor."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mayor Wetton."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:22:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:23:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.97,0:23:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe that the old man\Nand those kids were the same age?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that if we get the\Nship going, we can get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we be doing that without Nami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.88,0:23:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably upset\Nabout being left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be a wrinkly\Nold woman by now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything so chilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.22,0:23:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thoughts of Home!\NThe Pirate Graveyard of No Escape!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
